name: NonPhysicianEncounter
title: Non Physician Encounter
description: Codes representing possible values for encounters where the presence of physician or qualified healthcare provider may not be necessary

concept.display: Office or other outpatient visit for the evaluation and management of an established patient, that may not require the presence of a physician or other qualified health care professional. Usually, the presenting problem(s) are minimal
